Dia. 02 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is very easy after seeing the answer.
\par Black's hane at 1 is the maek for the capturing race.
\par
\par After this move White is captured.
\par }
