Dia. 03 Practice Problem
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is another capturing race.
\par
\par \b Black to play\b0 .
\par Find the maek which captures the three White stones in the corner.
\par
\par If Black takes the White stone at A, White plays at B and Black is captured. It becomes eye vs. no eye.
\par
\par
\par }
