Dia. 04 Hane
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's hane at 1 is the maek.
\par White has two liberties and Black's liberties increased to three.
\par
\par Hane like this can be an excellent move in a capturing race.
\par
\par }
